													<SHORT-NAME>I2cDeviceAddress</SHORT-NAME>
													<DESC>
														<L-2 L="EN">This parameter specifies the address of a slave device which is accessed by the master.

Note: Values bigger than 0x7F (127) lead to Extended Addressing.</L-2>
													</DESC>
													<ADMIN-DATA>
