												<ECUC-INTEGER-PARAM-DEF UUID="e9cf288c-2ff9-4e61-95e4-1729bbc5c67a">
													<SHORT-NAME>I2cDefaultData</SHORT-NAME>
													<DESC>
														<L-2 L="EN">This parameter specifies the default value of the channel.

Note: The default data is transmitted in case of TxBuffer and RxBuffer of the channel is set to NULL_PTR (e.g. via API I2c_SetupEB).</L-2>
													</DESC>
