														<L-4 L="EN">Priority of a sequence</L-4>
													</LONG-NAME>
													<DESC>
														<L-2 L="EN">This parameter specifies the priority of a sequence. Going from 0 (highest)  to 255 (lowest).</L-2>
													</DESC>
