											<SHORT-NAME>I2cPeripheralRegion</SHORT-NAME>
											<DESC>
												<L-2 L="EN">Reference to a I2cPeripheralRegion defined in the OS.
Only necessary, if the I2cProtectedMode is enabled.</L-2>
											</DESC>
											<LOWER-MULTIPLICITY>0</LOWER-MULTIPLICITY>
